'''New Escrow's Old Spaceport''' was the former main spaceport of [[New Escrow]] on [[Aargau/Legends|Aargau]]. It was here that [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Darth Vader]] destroyed [[Viscount (title)/Legends|Viscount]] [[Tardi]]'s [[Human replica droid|HRD]] replica.

It was later converted into a history museum.

